or: #1a1a1a; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 1em 0;"><span>=
The reason I bring it up is that it&#8217;s a good framing for a question I=
&#8217;ve been thinking a lot about. In my last essay pre-Maya, </span><em>=
<a href=3D"https://substack.com/redirect/732120eb-2dd5-4cce-98c7-0848a7293e=
1e?r=3D9p0gt" rel=3D"" style=3D"color: #1a1a1a; text-decoration: underline;=
