hape &#8211; physical versus digital &#8211; and that I wanted to spend tim=
e on paternity leave putting my finger on why that dichotomy was also dumb.=
 Instead of just physical abundance or a purely digital future, I want a co=
mbination of both: an </span><strong>Abundance Renaissance</strong><span>.<=
/span></p><p style=3D"color: #1a1a1a; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; m=
argin: 0 0 1em 0;"><span>As a quick and dirty shorthand, think about the </=
span><strong>Abundance Renaissance as the lovechild of the Renaissance, the=
