1a1a; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 1em 0;"><span>The per=
ception of a Great Stagnation over the past 50 years could be described as =
a shift from </span><strong>Working Harder</strong><span> (more energy usag=
e, more atoms innovation) to </span><strong>Working Smarter</strong><span> =
(better computing, more bits innovation).&#160;</span></p><p style=3D"color=
: #1a1a1a; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 1em 0;">My hunch=
